The '''Dead Rebels''' were a below average [[Band/Legends|band]] who performed in [[Mos Eisley/Legends|Mos Eisley]] following the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]]. One of their [[Music/Legends|songs]] was "[[Death Star Diva]]." The band consisted of a [[Klatooinian/Legends|Klatooinian]], a [[Talz/Legends|Talz]], and a [[Trandoshan/Legends|Trandoshan]].

